==English==

===Noun===
'''slugfest'''
#''(slang)'' A [[baseball]] [[game]] in which many [[runs]] are scored, especially by home runs
#: ''The game turned into a 15-9 '''slugfest'''.
#''(slang)'' A [[boxing]] [[match]] or fight marked by a heavy exchange of blows
#: ''The championship bout was a '''slugfest'''; both fighters were bloodied.

